gen, then provides broad consistency between homogeneous\nfibril radii and the lack of fibril nucleation during fibril growth.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2016 16:48:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-13"}
