olymer and disorder are constrained to\nhave equal numbers of renewals ($\\sigma_N=\\tau_N$), and one in which the\npolymer length is $\\tau_N$ rather than $\\sigma_N$. In both cases we show the\ncritical point is the same as in the original model, at least when $ \\alpha>0$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Aug 2016 19:42:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Apr 2017 21:05:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-28"}
